{"body":"Fixes #492.\n\n## Summary\n\n- Replace live crates.io/docs.rs status badges in generated GitHub release notes with static release-version artifact badges that still link to the exact crates.io and docs.rs version pages.\n- Restore the traditional README badge block for CI/CD, Desktop Release, crates.io, docs.rs, Rust version, Codecov, and license.\n- Preserve the issue #492 investigation, release evidence, screenshot, CI log, template comparison, and online research under `docs/case-studies/issue-492`.\n- Reported the matching Rust template docs.rs release-note badge issue upstream: link-foundation/rust-ai-driven-development-pipeline-template#85.\n\n## Evidence\n\nAffected release screenshot preserved in the branch:\n\n![Issue #492 badge screenshot](https://github.com/link-assistant/formal-ai/blob/issue-492-c714d50efef8/docs/case-studies/issue-492/assets/issue-screenshot.png?raw=true)\n\nCase study: https://github.com/link-assistant/formal-ai/blob/issue-492-c714d50efef8/docs/case-studies/issue-492/README.md\n\n## Tests\n\n- `cargo fmt --all -- --check`\n- `cargo test --test unit badges -- --nocapture`\n- `cargo test --test unit issue_492_release_badge_documents_are_traceable -- --nocapture`\n- `cargo test --test unit check_file_size -- --nocapture`\n- Manual `.rs`/`.lino` file-size threshold scan because `rust-script` was not installed locally\n- `cargo test --test unit` (1185 passed, 1 ignored)\n","commits":[{"authoredDate":"2026-06-28T17:15:51Z","authors":[{"email":"drakonard@gmail.com","id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE0MzE5MDQ=","login":"konard","name":"konard"}],"committedDate":"2026-06-28T17:15:51Z","messageBody":"Adding .gitkeep for PR creation (default mode).\nThis file will be removed when the task is complete.\n\nIssue: https://github.com/link-assistant/formal-ai/issues/492","messageHeadline":"Initial commit with task details","oid":"35fbfc5bed12615160bd73811f434719baa7ad26"},{"authoredDate":"2026-06-28T17:48:02Z","authors":[{"email":"drakonard@gmail.com","id":"MD